{"id":4163,"date":"2024-12-16T14:22:54","date_gmt":"2024-12-16T14:22:54","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=4163"},"modified":"2025-01-14T19:52:06","modified_gmt":"2025-01-14T19:52:06","slug":"plate-maker","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/plate-maker\/","title":{"rendered":"Plate Maker (NPC)"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td><strong>Seaport City<\/strong> &#8211; Inside Captain Davy\u2019s Shipyard at the Seaport City Harbor.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Purpose<\/th>\n<td>Gives you all types of creation plates in exchange for shards<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Transaction Item<\/th>\n<td>Shards (Red, Green, Blue, Yellow)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Cost<\/th>\n<td>(Varies)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Fly to the Seaport City Pokemon Center and follow the path east.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/01-pokemon-unbound-standing-outside-of-the-seaport-city-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Standing outside of the Seaport City Pokemon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Standing outside of the Seaport City Pokemon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Walk down the stairs and enter Captain Davy\u2019s Shipyard, just east of the KBT Expressway entrance.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/02-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-shipyard.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the Shipyard. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the Shipyard.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Plate Maker is the first NPC on the left behind a desk.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/03-pokemon-unbound-approaching-the-plate-maker.jpg\" alt=\"Approaching the Plate Maker. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Approaching the Plate Maker.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2>Purpose<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/04-pokemon-unbound-trading-shards-for-plates.jpg\" alt=\"Trading shards for plates. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Trading shards for plates.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Plate Maker converts shards into copies of Creation Plates that are used in acquiring <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/pokemon\/arceus\/\">Arceus<\/a>. However, the type and quantity of shards you\u2019ll need will depend on the kind of plate you want. <\/p>\n<p>The table below details all the plates that the Plate Maker can provide, alongside the required shards you\u2019ll need for each of them.<\/p>\n<table class=\"table grey left zebra\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Plate<\/th>\n<th>Required Shards<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Draco Plate<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>6 Red Shards<\/li>\n<li>2 Yellow Shards<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Dread Plate<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>2 Red Shards<\/li>\n<li>4 Blue Shards<\/li>\n<li>2 Green Shards<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Earth Plate<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>4 Red Shards<\/li>\n<li>2 Blue Shards<\/li>\n<li>2 Yellow Shards<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Fist Plate<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>6 Red Shards<\/li>\n<li>2 Yellow Shards<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Flame Plate<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>8 Red Shards<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Icicle Plate<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>4 Blue Shards<\/li>\n<li>4 Green Shards<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Insect Plate<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>6 Green Shards<\/li>\n<li>2 Yellow Shards<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Iron Plate<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>2 Red Shards<\/li>\n<li>2 Blue Shards<\/li>\n<li>2 Green Shards<\/li>\n<li>2 Yellow Shards<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Meadow Plate<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>8 Green Shards<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Mind Plate<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>4 Red Shards<\/li>\n<li>3 Blue Shards<\/li>\n<li>1 Green Shard<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Pixie Plate<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>6 Red Shards<\/li>\n<li>2 Blue Shards<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Sky Plate<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>6 Blue Shards<\/li>\n<li>2 Green Shards<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Splash Plate<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>8 Blue Shards<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Spooky Plate<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>2 Red Shards<\/li>\n<li>3 Blue Shards<\/li>\n<li>1 Green Shard<\/li>\n<li>2 Yellow Shards<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Stone Plate<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>4 Red Shards<\/li>\n<li>4 Yellow Shards<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Toxic Plate<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>4 Red Shards<\/li>\n<li>4 Blue Shards<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Zap Plate<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>8 Yellow Shards<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"299\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview.jpg 300w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">Useful NPCs<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":4164,"parent":2143,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false